{"tid":2098939,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"聯儲局副主席：可進一步推行寛鬆政策","createTime":"2020-07-08T00:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T07:30:43.000Z","uid":134415,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8814c07709ad0fefd283a22173d66dc0ab25123","tid":2098939,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:55:57.000Z","msg":"美國聯儲局副主席克拉里達表示，聯儲局已提供很大的政策寬鬆，但可以做得更多，將採取進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n他接受訪問時表示，聯儲局可以購買債券的規模沒有限制，亦可能透過前瞻指引進一步放寬政策，亦會維持對貸款的支持，<span style=\"color: red;\">需要多久就持續多久</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他提到，5月及6月經濟出現反彈跡象非常受歡迎，聯儲局正密切關注疫情發展，因為將決定經濟走勢。<br />\n<br />\n聯儲局一項調查顯示，美國人認為抵抗疫情及相關經濟影響的時間可能較預期長。有46%受訪者認為需要一年多才能恢復正常，比例較4月的調查高11個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536443-20200708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536443-20200708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivVhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=e6c833b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536443-20200708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fdd4f059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536443-20200708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9b7c6d905306d7e185b87bb0456b3f3339efd1d8","tid":2098939,"uid":5073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:24:55.000Z","msg":"Brrrrr"},{"pid":"317fab1444456f1595d37069a05d7fcfe03f83d5","tid":2098939,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgDVopy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgDVopy.jpg&h=c274b894&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"843b82c7e680be3c29fcfe8478c7c9e81c76116e","tid":2098939,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"印鈔機要加紙....."},{"pid":"5d64e8a00c4b33552aa6b3e94c7bd32960ecdb76","ti